@startuml Casos de Uso - Módulo de Ventas POS
!theme plain
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

title Módulo de Ventas - Sistema POS

' Actores
actor "Vendedor" as Seller
actor "Gerente" as Manager
actor "Administrador" as Admin

' Sistema
rectangle "Sistema de Ventas POS" {
  usecase "Registrar Venta" as UC1
  usecase "Consultar Ventas" as UC2
  usecase "Generar Reportes" as UC3
  usecase "Ver Dashboard" as UC4
  usecase "Cancelar Venta" as UC5
  usecase "Gestionar Órdenes\nE-commerce" as UC6
}

' Relaciones
Seller --> UC1
Seller --> UC2

Manager --> UC1
Manager --> UC2
Manager --> UC3
Manager --> UC4
Manager --> UC5
Manager --> UC6

Admin --> UC1
Admin --> UC2
Admin --> UC3
Admin --> UC4
Admin --> UC5
Admin --> UC6

' Nota explicativa
note right of UC1
  **Tipos de Venta:**
  - POS (tienda física)
  - E-commerce (online)
  - WhatsApp (redes sociales)
  
  Valida stock y actualiza
  inventario automáticamente
end note

note bottom of UC6
  **Estados:** PENDING → CONFIRMED
  → COMPLETED / CANCELLED
end note

@enduml
